---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import RelatedTools from '../../../components/RelatedTools.astro';

// Tool metadata
const name = "Code Formatter";
const category = "developer";
const tier = "Developer Tools";

// SEO metadata
const pageTitle = "Code Formatter - Prettify & Beautify JS, HTML, CSS, JSON Online";
const description = "Free easy code formatter online. Use our prettier code formatter to format and beautify HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and JSON code client-side inside your browser.";
const canonicalUrl = "https://toolkify.com/tools/developer/code-formatter";
const keywords = "code formatter, prettier code formatter, code formatter online, html code formatter, online code formatter, javascript code formatter, easy code formatter";
const ogImage = "/og/code-formatter.png";
---

<Layout 
  title={pageTitle}
  description={description}
  toolName={name}
  toolCategory={category}
  keywords={keywords}
  canonical={canonicalUrl}
  ogImage={ogImage}
  hideBanner={true}
>
  <!-- SEO JSON-LD WebApplication Schema -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "WebApplication",
      "name": "Code Formatter & Beautifier",
      "alternateName": "Client-Side Code Beautifier",
      "url": "https://toolkify.com/tools/developer/code-formatter",
      "description": "Format and beautify JS, HTML, CSS, and JSON inside your browser. Safe, private execution using Prettier in a background Web Worker.",
      "applicationCategory": "DeveloperApplication",
      "operatingSystem": "All",
      "browserRequirements": "Requires JavaScript. Requires HTML5.",
      "featureList": [
        "Beautify JavaScript, HTML, CSS, and JSON",
        "Configurable indentation sizes and quotes styles",
        "Web Worker execution to prevent UI freezing",
        "Syntax highlighting preview using Prism.js",
        "Detailed parsing error contexts with line highlight",
        "Snippet history log and shareable parameters URLs",
        "100% offline-ready local execution"
      ],
      "offers": {
        "@type": "Offer",
        "price": "0.00",
        "priceCurrency": "USD"
      }
    }
  </script>

  <!-- FAQ JSON-LD Schema -->
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": [
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How to write a code formatter?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>To write a code formatter, you typically start by writing a lexical analyzer (lexer) to convert the source text into tokens. Next, a parser organizes these tokens into an Abstract Syntax Tree (AST) representing the code structure. Finally, a printer traverses the AST and outputs clean text based on specific layout rules (like indentation limits and line lengths). Modern systems like Prettier also use a dynamic layout algorithm to wrap lines neatly depending on the configured print width.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What is a code formatter?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>A code formatter is an automated software utility that reformats source code files according to predefined style guides. It automatically manages indentation, line wrapping, spacing, brackets, braces, and quotes without altering the code's execution behavior. Using a formatter ensures code consistency across a project team and improves overall readability.</p>"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What are the benefits of using a code formatter?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "<p>The benefits of using a code formatter include: 1) Consistent code style across team members; 2) Increased readability and reduced cognitive load; 3) Time savings, as developers don't have to manually format code; 4) Fewer merge conflicts related to formatting styles; and 5) Easier detection of nested logical bugs due to proper visual layout indentation.</p>"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  </script>

  <!-- Prism.js & Theme CDN assets -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/themes/prism.min.css" />
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/prism.min.js" is:inline></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/components/prism-markup.min.js" is:inline></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/components/prism-css.min.js" is:inline></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/components/prism-javascript.min.js" is:inline></script>
  <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/prism/1.29.0/components/prism-json.min.js" is:inline></script>

  <section class="max-w-[1200px] w-full mx-auto px-4 py-3 sm:py-6 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:gap-4 animate-fade-in-up pb-16 print:p-0">
    <!-- Breadcrumb & Header -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 print:hidden">
      <nav class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] font-semibold text-slate uppercase" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Home</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-primary transition-colors">Tools</a>
        <span>/</span>
        <span class="text-brand-blue capitalize">{category}</span>
      </nav>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center justify-between mt-0.5 gap-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <h1 class="font-display font-medium text-xl sm:text-2xl tracking-tight text-primary">
            {name}
          </h1>
          <span class="bg-surface-pricing-featured text-brand-blue text-[10px] py-0.5 px-2 rounded-full font-semibold uppercase whitespace-nowrap shrink-0">{tier}</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
          <!-- Keyboard shortcuts reference -->
          <button
            type="button"
            id="shortcuts-btn"
            class="hidden sm:inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[11px] font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 bg-canvas hover:bg-surface border border-hairline text-slate hover:text-primary hover:border-primary/30 rounded-full hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-subtle"
            aria-label="View keyboard shortcuts"
          >
            <span>⌨ Keyboard Shortcuts</span>
          </button>

          <button
            type="button"
            id="share-btn"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 bg-canvas hover:bg-surface border border-hairline text-slate hover:text-primary hover:border-primary/30 rounded-full hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-subtle"
            aria-label="Share tool link"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.684 10.742l5.028-2.513m0 7.544l-5.028-2.513M18 8a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm-6 8a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 0a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
            </svg>
            <span>Share</span>
          </button>

          <button
            type="button"
            id="how-it-works-btn"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[11px] font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 bg-canvas hover:bg-surface border border-hairline text-slate hover:text-primary hover:border-primary/30 rounded-full hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-subtle"
            aria-label="How code formatter works"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-3.5 h-3.5"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2.5"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <span>How it works</span>
          </button>

          <button
            type="button"
            id="reset-btn"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[11px] font-semibold px-2.5 py-1 bg-canvas hover:bg-surface border border-hairline text-slate hover:text-brand-coral hover:border-brand-coral rounded-full hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-subtle"
            aria-label="Reset inputs and output"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              class="w-3 h-3"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2.5"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 1121.21 7.89M9 11l3-3 3 3m-3-3v12"
              ></path>
            </svg>
            <span>Reset</span>
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mobile Toggles (Shown on mobile/tablet only) -->
    <div class="flex lg:hidden rounded-full bg-surface p-0.5 border border-hairline w-full print:hidden">
      <button
        type="button"
        id="tab-input-btn"
        class="flex-1 text-center text-[11px] py-1.5 rounded-full font-bold transition-all cursor-pointer bg-primary text-canvas"
      >
        Input Editor
      </button>
      <button
        type="button"
        id="tab-output-btn"
        class="flex-1 text-center text-[11px] py-1.5 rounded-full font-bold transition-all cursor-pointer text-slate"
      >
        Formatted Output
      </button>
    </div>

    <!-- Workspace Board (Miro Rounded Board style) -->
    <div class="card-base p-3 sm:p-5 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:gap-4 print:border-none print:shadow-none print:bg-transparent print:p-0">
      
      <!-- Top Settings & Language Config Panel -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-3 sm:gap-4 pb-3 sm:pb-4 border-b border-hairline-soft items-end">
        
        <!-- Language Select & Auto-detect indication -->
        <div class="md:col-span-4 flex flex-col gap-1.5">
          <label for="language-select" class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate uppercase tracking-wider">Format Syntax</label>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <select id="language-select" class="text-input py-0.5 px-3 text-xs h-9 flex-grow cursor-pointer border border-hairline-strong bg-canvas rounded-md focus:outline-none focus:border-brand-blue">
              <option value="auto">⚡ Auto-detect Syntax</option>
              <option value="javascript">JavaScript (JS)</option>
              <option value="json">JSON</option>
              <option value="html">HTML Markup</option>
              <option value="css">CSS stylesheet</option>
            </select>
            <span id="detected-badge" class="hidden items-center justify-center bg-surface-yellow border border-yellow-light/80 text-yellow-dark text-[10px] font-bold px-2 rounded-md uppercase shrink-0">
              Auto: JSON
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Format Rules Config Box -->
        <div class="md:col-span-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 justify-start md:justify-end">
          
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
            <label for="indent-select" class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate uppercase">Spacing</label>
            <select id="indent-select" class="text-input py-0.5 px-2 text-xs h-9 cursor-pointer border border-hairline-strong bg-canvas rounded-md">
              <option value="2" selected>2 Spaces</option>
              <option value="4">4 Spaces</option>
              <option value="tabs">Tabs</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
            <label for="quote-select" class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate uppercase">Quotes</label>
            <select id="quote-select" class="text-input py-0.5 px-2 text-xs h-9 cursor-pointer border border-hairline-strong bg-canvas rounded-md">
              <option value="double" selected>Double ("")</option>
              <option value="single">Single ('')</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
            <label for="semi-select" class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate uppercase">Semicolons</label>
            <select id="semi-select" class="text-input py-0.5 px-2 text-xs h-9 cursor-pointer border border-hairline-strong bg-canvas rounded-md">
              <option value="true" selected>Always</option>
              <option value="false">Never</option>
            </select>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-1">
            <label class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate uppercase">Auto Format</label>
            <label class="relative inline-flex items-center h-9 cursor-pointer select-none">
              <input type="checkbox" id="auto-format-check" class="sr-only peer" checked />
              <div class="w-10 h-5 bg-hairline peer-focus:outline-none rounded-full peer peer-checked:after:translate-x-full peer-checked:after:border-white after:content-[''] after:absolute after:top-[10px] after:left-[2px] after:bg-white after:border-gray-300 after:border after:rounded-full after:h-4 after:w-4 after:transition-all peer-checked:bg-brand-blue"></div>
              <span class="ml-2 text-xs text-slate font-medium peer-checked:text-primary">Live</span>
            </label>
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Main Editor Panes -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-5 items-stretch relative">
        
        <!-- Left Pane: Input Editor -->
        <div id="pane-input" class="flex flex-col gap-2.5 print:hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-charcoal flex items-center gap-1.5 uppercase tracking-wider">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-brand-blue animate-pulse"></span>
              Source Code Input
            </span>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <button id="btn-load-js" class="text-[10px] font-bold text-brand-blue hover:underline cursor-pointer">JS Sample</button>
              <span class="text-stone">|</span>
              <button id="btn-load-html" class="text-[10px] font-bold text-brand-blue hover:underline cursor-pointer">HTML Sample</button>
              <span class="text-stone">|</span>
              <button id="btn-load-css" class="text-[10px] font-bold text-brand-blue hover:underline cursor-pointer">CSS Sample</button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Editor Wrapper -->
          <div 
            id="drop-zone" 
            class="relative flex-grow flex flex-col min-h-[250px] sm:min-h-[350px] lg:min-h-[460px] border border-hairline-strong rounded-xl bg-surface-soft transition-all focus-within:border-brand-blue focus-within:ring-2 focus-within:ring-brand-blue/10 overflow-hidden"
          >
            <!-- Drop message overlay -->
            <div id="drop-overlay" class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-blue/5 border-2 border-dashed border-brand-blue rounded-xl flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 opacity-0 pointer-events-none transition-all duration-200 z-10">
              <span class="text-2xl">📥</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-blue">Drop code file here</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Line Number Counter & Input Area -->
            <div class="flex flex-grow overflow-auto h-full max-h-[500px]">
              <div id="input-line-numbers" class="w-10 select-none text-right pr-2 py-3 text-[11px] font-mono text-stone border-r border-hairline-soft bg-surface/50 leading-5">
                1
              </div>
              <textarea
                id="code-input"
                class="flex-grow p-3 font-mono text-[12px] bg-transparent text-primary resize-none outline-none leading-5 min-h-[300px] overflow-y-hidden"
                placeholder="Paste code snippet here, or drag & drop a file (HTML, CSS, JS, JSON)..."
                aria-label="Source Code Input"
                spellcheck="false"
              ></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-[11px] font-semibold text-slate">
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:text-primary cursor-pointer">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-brand-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-8l-4-4m0 0l-4 4m4-4v12"></path>
              </svg>
              <span>Upload Local File</span>
              <input type="file" id="file-uploader" class="hidden" accept=".js,.jsx,.ts,.tsx,.json,.html,.css" />
            </label>
            <span id="char-counter" class="font-mono text-stone">0 chars | 0 lines</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Pane: Formatted Output -->
        <div id="pane-output" class="hidden lg:flex flex-col gap-2.5 min-h-[250px] sm:min-h-[350px] lg:min-h-[460px]">
          
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-bold text-charcoal uppercase tracking-wider">Beautified Result</span>
            
            <!-- Actions panel -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
              <button
                type="button"
                id="btn-copy"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-semibold px-2.5 py-1.5 bg-canvas hover:bg-surface border border-hairline text-slate hover:text-primary hover:border-primary/30 rounded-full hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-subtle"
                title="Copy code to clipboard"
              >
                Copy
              </button>
              <button
                type="button"
                id="btn-download"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-semibold px-2.5 py-1.5 bg-canvas hover:bg-surface border border-hairline text-slate hover:text-primary hover:border-primary/30 rounded-full hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-subtle"
                title="Download formatted code file"
              >
                Download
              </button>
              <button
                type="button"
                id="btn-share"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-[10px] font-semibold px-2.5 py-1.5 bg-canvas hover:bg-surface border border-hairline text-slate hover:text-primary hover:border-primary/30 rounded-full hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all cursor-pointer shadow-subtle"
                title="Share link encoding parameters"
              >
                Share Snippet
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Highlight Output View -->
          <div class="relative flex-grow flex flex-col border border-hairline rounded-xl bg-surface overflow-hidden min-h-[200px] sm:min-h-[300px] lg:min-h-[460px]">
            <!-- Toast notification inside codebox -->
            <div id="toast-message" class="absolute top-3 right-3 bg-success-accent text-canvas text-[10px] font-bold py-1.5 px-3 rounded-md shadow-subtle opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-300 pointer-events-none z-20">
              Copied!
            </div>

            <!-- Prettier Loading Indicator overlay -->
            <div id="loading-overlay" class="hidden absolute inset-0 bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-xs flex-col items-center justify-center gap-2 z-10 transition-opacity duration-300">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 border-4 border-brand-blue border-t-transparent rounded-full animate-spin"></div>
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate">Initializing formatting engine...</span>
            </div>

            <!-- Formatted code rendering pre-container -->
            <pre class="m-0 p-4 overflow-auto h-full max-h-[500px] leading-5 w-full select-all outline-none bg-transparent"><code id="output-code" class="font-mono text-[12px] block"></code></pre>
          </div>

          <!-- Action status bar -->
          <div class="flex items-center justify-end">
            <button
              type="button"
              id="btn-format"
              class="lg:flex button-primary text-xs py-2 px-6 !rounded-full shadow-subtle hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all cursor-pointer font-bold gap-2 items-center"
            >
              <span>Format Code</span>
              <kbd class="hidden sm:inline px-1 py-0.2 bg-canvas/20 rounded font-mono text-[9px]">Ctrl+Enter</kbd>
            </button>
          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Real-Time status panel -->
      <div class="border-t border-hairline-soft pt-4 mt-2 flex flex-col gap-3">
        <!-- Execution summary info banner -->
        <div id="status-banner" class="p-2.5 rounded-lg border flex items-center justify-between text-[11px] transition-all duration-300 bg-surface-yellow border-yellow-light/80 text-yellow-dark">
          <span id="status-msg" class="font-bold flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-yellow-dark animate-pulse"></span>
            Ready. Waiting for syntax payload...
          </span>
          <span id="status-perf" class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold"></span>
        </div>

        <!-- Precise syntax failure trace overlay -->
        <div id="error-trace-panel" class="hidden p-3 rounded-lg border border-brand-red-dark bg-brand-red text-xs text-coral-dark leading-relaxed flex flex-col gap-1.5 animate-shake">
          <div class="font-bold flex items-center gap-1.5">
            <span>⚠️ Format Parse Exception:</span>
            <span id="error-brief" class="font-semibold text-primary"></span>
          </div>
          <pre id="error-context" class="font-mono text-[11px] p-2 bg-canvas/60 rounded border border-brand-red-dark/30 whitespace-pre overflow-x-auto text-primary"></pre>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <RelatedTools currentSlug="code-formatter" />

    <!-- History Panel -->
    <div class="card-base flex flex-col gap-3 p-4 sm:p-5 mt-2">
      <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-xs sm:text-sm text-primary flex items-center gap-1.5">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4 text-brand-blue" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
        </svg>
        Recent Snippets History
      </h3>
      <div id="history-container" class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <span class="text-[11px] text-stone">Snippets formatted on this device will be stored in your browser.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Security statement footer -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] text-slate px-1 print:hidden">
      <span class="flex items-center gap-1">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-3 h-3 text-success-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
        </svg>
        100% Client-Side Sandbox, zero server tracking.
      </span>
      <span>v2.1.0</span>
    </div>

    <!-- SEO Content & FAQ Section -->
    <section class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-8 border-t border-hairline pt-10" aria-label="About this code formatter">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-2xl sm:text-3xl tracking-tight text-primary">
          Easy Code Formatter Online for Clean, Standardized Syntax
        </h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed">
          In modern software engineering, clean and standardized code is essential for maintainability, readability, and seamless team collaboration. A high-quality <strong>code formatter</strong> saves time by automating the formatting decisions that would otherwise spark endless debate during peer reviews. Our <strong>online code formatter</strong> acts as an <strong>easy code formatter</strong> that supports multiple popular languages including JavaScript, HTML, CSS, and JSON. Rather than manually indenting nested logic, adjusting line wraps, or double-checking bracket configurations, you can paste your raw code block directly into our secure workspace and get a structured, professional output instantly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-primary">
            Private Client-Side Prettier Code Formatter
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate leading-relaxed">
            What makes this utility stand out is its reliance on the industry-standard <strong>prettier code formatter</strong> engine running completely within your browser. Because the compilation is executed inside a local Web Worker thread, your code never travels over the internet or touches any remote database. This makes our <strong>code formatter online</strong> 100% private and secure for use with proprietary enterprise scripts, sensitive data files, and commercial codebases. The Web Worker execution model guarantees that formatting large code scripts won't freeze your browser tab, ensuring a smooth, fluid user experience every time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h3 class="font-display font-semibold text-lg text-primary">
            Multi-Language Formatting Capabilities
